  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Almost every major life event as an expat in Vietnam — getting a work permit, starting a business, getting married, enrolling kids in school — requires authenticated documents. The process involves multiple steps across multiple countries, and getting one step wrong means starting over.
  </p>
  <p>
